{"tid":1919672,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有d特別恐怖既真故事分享","createTime":"2020-03-11T02:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T09:12:38.000Z","uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6bf6786fd95b7ce60f3ed7f38432603cf22252","tid":1919672,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"我分享先 細個聽家姐講 無咩人知既應該  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係外國有對夫妻買左個娃娃比個女 點知個娃娃原來係中左咒 有鬼既 搞到個屋企成日比野搞 最後要請神父驅鬼先搞得掂 好似隻隻娃娃仲係神父屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個聽完訓唔到 好恐怖 家姐話係外國讀書既朋友屋企發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e5b928e89ed60cb02c6a59169d02f868cb7c8f","tid":1919672,"uid":81783,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你體內有武漢肺炎病毒潛伏期"},{"pid":"7142df7773c40d42a25d68ff8915ba78dc773b3a","tid":1919672,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"認真post"},{"pid":"707b43ea5ca79d0cc4176a55d5ad4bd09f93cbbb","tid":1919672,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf841a429c1cad55059ff53095d04cf0f2a02fa","tid":1919672,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"由出世開始到而家32歲都未食過一餐飽飯，咁多年黎最好餸就係一隻咸蛋加一碗裝滿既白飯再加多半磚腐乳。<br />\n<br />\n住係深水埗，未離開過九龍，最遠係18歲果年去過牛頭角搞身份證。<br />\n未行入過大商場，好怕D保安趕我出黎<br />\n<br />\n同一件衫着左二十年，細個專登買大D，就一路着到20歲因為爛到屋企都搵唔到布補番先去買左件二手衫既，果晚都已經開心到訓唔着。<br />\n<br />\n試過有個月窮到冇錢開飯，要落M記食D OL食剩既二手薯條，俾人趕俾人屌乜都試過，但係我真係好肚餓，肚餓果陣尊嚴唔可以當飯食。<br />\n<br />\n有一次病左，唔敢去睇急症，因為身上連一百蚊都冇，去到最後病到要訓醫院，醒番我都即刻偷走，因為我俾唔起住院費。<br />\n<br />\n每年新年前要提心吊膽，因為好驚食環署黎洗地，地下濕左，我就冇地方訓。<br />\n<br />\n16歲果年鐘意左個女同學，膽粗粗同佢表白，俾佢一巴車埋塊面到，佢講左句:「你呢D連沐浴露都買唔起既垃圾唔好再痴埋黎。」<br />\n的確，我連沐浴露係咩味道都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n19歲果年為左試下洗頭水沐浴露係咩味，用哂果個月既零用錢入去泳池，執人用淨既細細枝果D 洗頭水同沐浴露，第一次聞到果陣味，我係個更衣室到喊左出黎，周圍D人望住我大大力咁索枝 dove，我19歲先知洗頭水原來係咩味道。"},{"pid":"340085275433243d2bdf566f75371f2e946e989d","tid":1919672,"uid":266382,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"小姐你貴姓？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你初步測試程陽性"},{"pid":"55d09e29c8ba5c56735438655e0d9c17176f666d","tid":1919672,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"孫楊d尿紫色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bee1c1b7e8172dca57288cd84a2e478880940d","tid":1919672,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"721 831<br />\n夠未"},{"pid":"0c84387d6fb961cd3165176f2151531885fcac46","tid":1919672,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"林<br />\n鄭<br />\n月<br />\n娥"},{"pid":"33824b5b833e70ea8608e8ef68f99134ae3fe61e","tid":1919672,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"加多個<br />